des:
Old Skool Rave Tapes is a 24/7 streaming radio station showcasing the finest in rave tapes from yesteryear.

All sets have either been personally ripped by us or downloaded via the web – big respect to all the tape rippers keeping the sound alive!

The sole aim of this station is to keep the old skool thriving and preserve rave scene history.
